## Job Title: Marketing Associate (Fresher)

## About AICORP

AICORP is a research-driven company based in Trivandrum, founded in 2020. We specialize in developing innovative products that solve real-world problems through technology. Our flagship platforms include Buyconn, Street XP, and Breakthrough Innovation Labs (BIL).

**Job Summary** 
We’re looking for enthusiastic and self-motivated Marketing Associates to join our dynamic team. As a fresher, you will gain hands-on experience in branding, digital marketing, content creation, campaign management, and customer engagement. You will support the marketing team in planning and executing initiatives that promote our brand, products, and services to targeted audiences.

**Key Responsibilities**
- Assist in the development and execution of marketing campaigns.
- Support social media content creation and daily management.
- Conduct market research to identify trends and opportunities.
- Help organize promotional events and partner activities.
- Monitor performance of marketing initiatives and prepare reports.
- Collaborate with design, sales, and product teams for campaign execution.
- Gather feedback and suggestions from users and partners.

**Required Qualifications**
- A bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Business, Communication, or a related field.
- Strong verbal and written communication skills.
- Confidence in presenting ideas and interacting with internal and external teams.
- Familiarity with social media platforms and digital tools.
- Passion for branding, storytelling, and customer engagement.
- Willingness to learn, adapt, and take initiative.

**Compensation**
- Stipend during Probation (3 months): ₹5,000 – ₹7,500/month (based on performance & skillset)
- Post-Probation: Salary will be revised based on performance and aligned with industry standards.

**Why Join Us?**
- Work in an innovative, fast-paced environment.
- Hands-on training and mentorship.
- Real impact and visibility on active projects.
- Opportunities for rapid growth and skill development.

 Location: Trivandrum, Kerala
 Employment Type: Full-Time
 Department: Marketing
 Company: AICORP (Aziz Industries Corporation)
